response.overview: Everyone's invited to the Sesame Street Dance Along. Join Big Bird, Gina, Mike, Count, Bert, Hoots the Owl, and "the kids" as they show us different types of dances. And you can do your own thing with "The Any Way You Fell Dance." All in all, there are nine terrific dances that are sure to make everyone want to dance along.
response.title: Sesame Songs: Dance Along!
